Title: Plasson 7438 adaptor table X and Y 25 x 22mm Copper
Description: Made of polypropylene (PP), this Plasson 7438 25 x 22mm compression reducing adapter for copper pipes is ideal for use in systems used for conveying water and other fluids in urban and inter-urban infrastructure, industrial, mining, landscape, and farming applications, replacing and existing connection with a watertight, leak-free compression fit. Made of durable, stress-resistant material, this adapter is machined to withstand 16 bar pressure and while not suitable for hot water systems can cope with sub-zero temperatures.
